      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "ORIGINAL POINT"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The most successful people believe in themselves almost to the point of delusion. Self-belief must be balanced with self-awareness."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
