      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "ORIGINAL POINT"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Original thinking is very difficult to teach. Think from first principles. \"I will fail many times, and I will be really right once.\""
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": ""
      },
      {
